snippet.title: Record of Lodoss War ~Deedlit in Wonder Labyrinth~ Full Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Deedlit in Wonder Labyrinth is finally here.
Deedlit's epic adventure is about to come to a close.
Witness battles with Narse, Beld, Ashram, and more deadly foes, rendered in beautiful pixel art!
And finally...
Experience the end of this wonderful tale for yourself.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1203630/_/
